<h2>Tools</h2>
<p>
Command-line tool to post Pastit.
</p>
<h3>SetUp</h3>
<p>
Download: <a href="{{$config.url}}download">pastit</a>
</p>
Add <pre class="inline-pre">~/bin</pre> directory to your PATH. (or it's alright that install to <pre class="inline-pre">/usr/local/bin</pre> etc.)
<pre>
$ wget -O ~/bin/pastit {{$config.url}}download
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/pastit
$ echo "token={{$app.user.token}}" > ~/.pastit
</pre>

<h3>Usage</h3>

Paste file:
<pre>
$ pastit hoge.php
</pre>

Paste with stdin:
<pre>
$ diff -u a.txt b.txt | pastit
</pre>

Paste with stdin (type specified):
<pre>
$ git diff hoge.php master..origin/master | pastit -t diff
</pre>
